类 RdmaCqProcessor<C extends RdmaEndpoint>

    RdmaActiveCqProcessor

    public abstract class RdmaCqProcessor<C extends RdmaEndpoint>
extends RdmaCqProvider
implements Runnable
    Extends the raw RdmaCqClient with active processing of CQ events. This class has an event loop querying the CQ and delivering event to a ICqConsumer.
